    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m super excited to find a new home for my trusty ride! \ud83d\ude97 It\u2019s been such a reliable companion for me and still runs like a dream. It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still in really solid shape for all your upcoming road trips. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it handles. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS system. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power to the rear wheels through a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS overhaul. The chassis remains composed with a well-sorted suspension geometry that preserves the car\u2019s legendary handling characteristics. While it bears the honest patina of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road, the mechanical vitals are robust, and the engine pulls strongly through the entire rev range. A mechanically sound example of one of the finest analog driving machines ever engineered.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well maintained. Clean title. Runs well. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly captures the balance of performance and comfort. The exterior retains a beautiful, deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the upholstery is free of tears or heavy stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free and vibrant. All power features, including the heated seats, sunroof, and premium audio system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is sound\u2014the engine pulls strongly with no hesitation, the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable, and the suspension remains taut over uneven pavement. It has been garage-kept by a non-smoker and has a documented history of regular oil changes and scheduled maintenance. This is a solid, reliable vehicle that looks great and drives even better, offering a premium experience without the premium price tag.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This specimen has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and safety. Featuring a documented service history and a well-preserved interior, it offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning professional. We invite you to experience the refined balance of luxury and utility this exceptional model provides.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape, ready to hit the road for many more miles. It drives beautifully and has been well-loved, making it the perfect pick if you want something dependable without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019m super excited for someone else to enjoy it as much as I have\u2014drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for structural integrity. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and Bilstein dampers. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential lock. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all cylinders remain within tight factory tolerances. A true driver's spec for those who value tactile feedback and high-revving naturally aspirated performance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
